»CL9:                    s c e n e   s t r i k e   f o u r
»CL8:                         the official invitation
»CL7:                         [ english version two ]

»CL0:    did  you  know that there is a demo scene in yugoslavia?  did you know
that  just  in  the  last two years, 6 demo parties were held in belgrade?
can  you  allow  yourself  to  miss  another  one?  maybe so, but THIS ONE
surelly no ;>>>

    scene  strike  4 [also known as ss4] is computer demo party which will
be  held  in  April,  3th  and  4th  1999 in cinema rex cultural center in
belgrade.  like our previous organised events, we tend to make even better
and more interesting scene party for both attendants and compo winners.





















»CL9:                             f e a t u r e s

»CL0:    beside 'tradional' competitions in computer demos, intros, animations,
graphics and music, ss4 prepares:
    »CL1:-»  concert with yugoslav scene and non-scene musicians.  this event is
being prepared with nexus organization from indjija, so you better prepare
yourself  for  some  serious mindshit.  it will also be visually supported
with realtime demo mix which will be done by corrosion posse.

    »CL1:-»  update  special  demo  showdown,  presenting  new  concept  of demo
showdowns.

    »CL1:-» local network with internet access.

    »CL1:-»  tradional  contents  like normal demo projection and networked game
consoles will be again available to everyone interested in abusing them ;>
quake  tournaments  and  similar  mass  gaming  crap  nonsense will NOT be
organized,  the gamers are definitelly not going to have nice time on ss4.
scene strike is DEMO PARTY which aims to gather and to support DEMO SCENE,
and plans to keep that hardline.




















»CL0:    there  will  be no computers available for public usage, so you better
pack  yourself on time, and bring your computer along with you in order to
be a real party member and not JAFO ;> we are receiving table reservations
in  the  ASAP  manner, because there is a limited amount of tables, so act
now, and reserve yours on time!

    local  network  and internet will be present and available, but always
keep  in  mind  that  their  primary use is for the party and its realtime
presence  on  the net.  problems caused by the local game seasons will not
be tolerated.

    entrance  fee  is 30 yugoslav dinars [3-4 DEM] and is valid during the
whole party time.  girls also pay - in the spirit of equal rights.



























»CL9:                        f o o d   &   d r i n k s

»CL0:    during  scene  strike  4 party, little bar will be open in cinema rex,
but  since  rex  is  located  in  the city, there won't be any problems in
getting  any other food or drink or anything in any time of day and night.
there  are  plenty  of  shops  and fast food restaurants working round the
clock.   drinks are not forbidden, but bottled drinks are not permitted to
bring in, because of various reasons...

    if  you  are by any chance organizing some group trip from the far [or
even  from  abroad]  please  drop  us  note  over email, so we could maybe
organize some help!




























